{% set org_label = report.org if report.org else "" %}
{% set user_label = report.user if report.user else "" %}
# GitHub Activity Report {{ org_label }} {{ user_label }}

Generated at: {{ report.generated_at.isoformat() }}
Period: {{ report.since.date().isoformat() }} to {{ report.until.date().isoformat() }}

## Summary

- Organization: {{ report.org or "N/A" }}
- User: {{ report.user or "N/A" }}
- Repositories: {{ report.activity.repositories|length }}
- Commits: {{
    report.activity.repositories.values()
      | map(attribute="commits")
      | sum
  }} (lines: {{
    report.activity.repositories.values()
      | map(attribute="lines_added")
      | sum
  }}++ / {{
    report.activity.repositories.values()
      | map(attribute="lines_deleted")
      | sum
  }}--)
- Pull requests: opened {{
    report.activity.repositories.values()
      | map(attribute="pull_requests_opened")
      | sum
  }}, merged {{
    report.activity.repositories.values()
      | map(attribute="pull_requests_merged")
      | sum
  }}
- Issues: opened {{
    report.activity.repositories.values()
      | map(attribute="issues_opened")
      | sum
  }}, closed {{
    report.activity.repositories.values()
      | map(attribute="issues_closed")
      | sum
  }}
- Active contributors: {{ report.activity.active_contributors|length }} (inactive: {{ report.activity.inactive_contributors|length }})

## Contributors

{% for login, summary in report.activity.users.items() %}
### @{{ login }}

- Commits: {{ summary.commits }} ({{ summary.lines_added }}++ / {{ summary.lines_deleted }}--)
- Pull requests: opened {{ summary.pull_requests_opened }}, merged {{ summary.pull_requests_merged }}
- Issues: opened {{ summary.issues_opened }}, closed {{ summary.issues_closed }}, assigned {{ summary.issues_assigned }}
- Reviews: given {{ summary.reviews_given }}, received {{ summary.reviews_received }}

{% endfor %}

## Repositories

{% for name, summary in report.activity.repositories.items() %}
### {{ name }}

- Commits: {{ summary.commits }} ({{ summary.lines_added }}++ / {{ summary.lines_deleted }}--)
- Pull requests: opened {{ summary.pull_requests_opened }}, merged {{ summary.pull_requests_merged }}
- Issues: opened {{ summary.issues_opened }}, closed {{ summary.issues_closed }}
- Contributors: {{ summary.contributors }}

{% endfor %}

## Activity timeline

| Day | Commits | Pull requests | Issues |
| --- | ------- | ------------- | ------ |
{% for bucket in report.timelines.by_day %}
| {{ bucket.day.isoformat() }} | {{ bucket.commits }} | {{ bucket.pull_requests }} | {{ bucket.issues }} |
{% endfor %}

## Pull requests

| # | Repository | Author | State | Created | Merged | Title |
| - | ---------- | ------ | ----- | ------- | ------ | ----- |
{% for pr in report.pull_requests
     | sort(attribute="created_at", reverse=True) %}
| {{ pr.number }} | {{ pr.repository_full_name }} | {{ pr.author_login or "unknown" }} | {%- if pr.is_merged -%}merged{%- else -%}{{ pr.state|lower }}{%- endif -%} | {{ pr.created_at.date().isoformat() }} | {{ pr.merged_at.date().isoformat() if pr.merged_at else "" }} | {{ pr.title }} |
{% endfor %}

## Commits

| When | Repository | Author | Message | Lines |
| ---- | ---------- | ------ | ------- | ----- |
{% for commit in report.commits
     | sort(attribute="committed_at", reverse=True) %}
| {{ commit.committed_at.isoformat() }} | {{ commit.repository_full_name }} | {{ commit.author_login or commit.author_name or "unknown" }} | {{ commit.message_headline }} | {{ commit.additions }}++ / {{ commit.deletions }}-- |
{% endfor %}

## Issues

| # | Repository | Author | State | Created | Closed | Assignees | Title |
| - | ---------- | ------ | ----- | ------- | ------ | --------- | ----- |
{% for issue in report.issues
     | sort(attribute="created_at", reverse=True) %}
| {{ issue.number }} | {{ issue.repository_full_name }} | {{ issue.author_login or "unknown" }} | {{ issue.state|lower }} | {{ issue.created_at.date().isoformat() }} | {{ issue.closed_at.date().isoformat() if issue.closed_at else "" }} | {%- if issue.assignee_logins -%}{{ issue.assignee_logins | join(", ") }}{%- endif -%} | {{ issue.title }} |
{% endfor %}

